MerbRJS
=======

Merb plugin that enables you to use 'page' object in your controllers like RJS of Rails


Example
=======

app/views/top/index.html.erb :
  <div id="message"></div>
  <div id="content"></div>
  <%= link_to "update", "refresh", :onclick=>"$.getScript(this.href);return false;" %>

app/controllers/top.rb :
  class Top < Application
    def refresh
      page[:message].text Time.now
      page[:content].html "<font color=red>Updated!</font>"
      display page
    end
  end

http://localhost:4000/top/refresh :
  $("#message").text("2008-11-30T08:33:12+09:00");
  $("#content").html("<font color=red>Updated!<\/font>");


Install
=======

  It will be released in a few days!


